{"tid":507823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國玻璃心】「雪山獅子旗」餘波 中國U20男足杯葛德友誼賽","createTime":"2017-12-23T15:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T05:18:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5950312c8b0adea5f6e529b14d5d071799be6224","tid":507823,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T15:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171223/large/1514021437_2bff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171223%2Flarge%2F1514021437_2bff.jpg&h=393ec891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國U20選拔隊上月在德國比賽期間，遭到藏獨人士在看台展示「雪山獅子旗」，繼而引發中國足協中斷U20項目合作、安排隊伍返國後，德國足協（DFB）昨日發表聲明稱，經中德足協雙方協商達成共識，中國隊將不再參加剩餘賽事。<br />\n<br />\n聲明稱，早在11月24日，這一基於西南地區聯賽各俱樂部自願參加的比賽就已被暫停，所有剩余餘賽事當時被推遲至冬歇期之後。在與德國美因茨隊比賽之後，中德足協雙方決定暫停比賽。在這場比賽中，中國隊暫時離場，以回應球場上出現的「雪山獅子旗」。<br />\n<br />\n中國足協當時發出聲明，認為體育賽事不應受到非體育因素的干擾，出現這樣的事情既不符合兩國發展友好關係的基本原則，也不符合國際足總的相關規定。中國足協表示，國家核心利益不能因任何原因受到損害，因此決定中斷U20項目合作，並安排隊伍回國。中國足協將總結經驗教訓，繼續大力推動國際交流合作，不斷提高中國足球水平。<br />\n<br />\n當時，德國媒體認為，中國U20男足可能不會再到德國，而德國足協或許面臨賠償問題。據《世界報》稱，德國足協正在努力遏制項目終止後的損失，這將影響到中德足球「廣泛合作協議」，該合作讓德國球會和相關企業順利進入擁有5億球迷的中國大市場，在掛旗事件的影響下，德國很可能被英國或意大利代替。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171223/57618827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F57618827&d=YOYowMKT4GHpmLnXTDE8RqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=88f6effa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F57618827&h=a3d96054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171223/57618827</a>"},{"pid":"d81c7d3801ad8ceb77c101d871f1e6a7361038ec","tid":507823,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb00bc9ac7c0a5f531891fcaf9224431f165296","tid":507823,"uid":64689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"自己主動要人陪你踢，唔順氣要返歸，咁就唔叫杯葛啦"},{"pid":"3978dd59b015408748d3dc30ddc9d86bd33760c4","tid":507823,"uid":127123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"中國外交部長王毅支持巴勒斯坦立國,但國外出示雪山獅子旗就發惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d42053a54f555625ae43fcb957191d27e11ad1","tid":507823,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"藏獨人士奧運識做啦<br />\n唔好再攪破壞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b57656ba4b2946560e8a33fb4ba68c8f461989","tid":507823,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:49:52.000Z","msg":"足球依d西方運動<br />\n小小支那學咩人踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b070bbb17e7cf754157ee36ea87c55c4d665db0","tid":507823,"uid":32588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T03:55:09.000Z","msg":"以後有中港大戰就拎雪山獅子旗入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee92b978da38d56f49dabed105fd7880329a07e1","tid":507823,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"支那學乜野踢波丫，垃圾人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}